The player begins in the first area with a single Battle Toad, whoever was in the last slot in the party (not counting The Blyatt Knight). The objective is to locate the other two party members and then defeat the Dream Drug Dealers. The quickest way to do this is to enter the left-hand door in the first area, retrieve the first party member, and then enter the door here. The next area has two doors, enter the upper-right one, then take the right door. Rescue the third party member and enter the door, then go left and enter the door in the middle of the large platform to reach a new area, open the door to confront Captain Benchode. 
